data.description: Seller is offering a $9,000 buyers credit for closing costs or rate buy down! This two-story brick was built to be a forever home with no expense spared! From the whirlpool tubs to the solid core doors you do not want to miss this rare opportunity. The house features 3 spacious bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and a large bonus room over the expansive 2 car garage. With an additional detached garage and over 3,100 sqft of living space this home has something for everyone. The approx 1.9-acre lot offers a country setting and is conveniently located close to i-75, directly behind the Glen Alpine subdivision. Only Approx 7mi to Norris Dam Marina. Call to schedule your showing today!
